      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWBOURNE CALI (7) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 30.24 to score two back then following on with a 30.35 win over 525m at this track. In form and can measure up again. KIWI HARRY (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (30.38) in a Grade 5 at Wentworth Park. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including two wins, from four starts. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PHOENIX VIOLET (3) failed to feature last start after missing the jump at this track, but prior to that won by a neck at this track (23.12) beating Boracay Beauty in a Grade 5 on February 13. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. In the mix. FLY HIGH HENRY (6) looks an each-way chance.",
